This download contains all 3 Among Us maps. The Skeld, MiraHQ and Polus are all rebuilt in Minecraft. You can mess around in these maps or even play PvP on it.
The Skeld:
The Skeld is the original Among Us map with the infamous Electrical.
MiraHQ is the first DLC Among Us map set in a massive skyscraper and a vent system that connects the entire map.

Polus:
Polus is the most recent and biggest map set on a outer space planet.

title: Void World

crawledImageUrls.text:
Custom Void World map for whatever you need. It is a world filled of well? void. I searched for Void World?s on MCBE and I came across nothing that was easy to download, so I decided to make one for myself and the community.
Bedrock Edition currently doesn?t have custom flat worlds, so you can use this Void World for whatever you may need. Examples: You can make a parkour map over the void, make a floating server spawn, or anything! Enjoy.
The World is entirely made up of Void except for the exception of one bedrock block located at the coordinates, (0, 50, 0).
If you encounter any bugs with the Download, the world, or with world generation problems please let me know down in the comments.

title: Parkour (Nether Edition)
briefDescription: Hi! This is my first submission on MCPEDL, so I decided to make some good ol' nether parkour. There are four levels, each varying in ...

crawledImageUrls.text:
Hi! This is my first submission on MCPEDL, so I decided to make some good ol? nether parkour.
There are four levels, each varying in difficulty from easy to insane. Each level is based on a nether aspect, such as nether fortresses and forests.
This is nether themed parkour. Have you ever thought: ?There is not enough good parkour in the world.?? This is fast, easygoing nether parkour. It is quick, maybe takes around 20 minutes for a beginner to complete it, and it is great for YouTube videos.
Speaking of You Tube, here is a link to my YouTube channel : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEUGYEQ45AcU9pCJuOOnF7Q
It is meant to be done without stopping, but it is not speed parkour. Each level has a different color scheme and theme.
Each level is themed on the nether, with four different difficulty levels and four different themes.
Here is the first level, easy nether fortress. It is only regular jumps, no ladders or shulker box jumps. There are 2 checkpoints.
FRONT VIEW:

This is the second level, Crimson Forest. It is medium difficulty, with regular jumps, ladder jumps, and slime jumps. There are 2 checkpoints, one in the beginning and one in the end. It is
FRONT VIEW:
BACK VIEW:

This is level 3. It is warped forest themed. It is difficulty hard, with 2 checkpoints, regular jumps, and ladder jumps.
FRONT VIEW:

This is level 4, Hard nether fortress. It is difficulty insane. There are ladder jumps, shulker box jumps, slime jumps, and regular jumps. There is only one checkpoint.
FRONT VIEW:
BACK VIEW:

This is my second map. Not far from my first map, it is still a survival puzzle genre. But with a little horror, calm no jumpscare :).
The horror of this map is not from ghosts or monsters, but from a slightly dark atmosphere.
Now we will discuss about the story line. You guys are the one who has amnesia, but he really wants to go to the cave. But while in the cave he forgot his memories and had to find a way out.
And now we will see what is on the map:
-From the picture above, you will be in a very large ravine.
-From the second picture, you will enter a very dark cave. You will only be provided with flint & steel.

title: Dimensions Parkour
briefDescription: Do you want an epic parkour map to play on your own and with friends! Welcome to Dimensions Parkour! This is a parkour map that ...

crawledImageUrls.text:
Do you want an epic parkour map to play on your own and with friends! Welcome to Dimensions Parkour! This is a parkour map that takes you through all of the 3 dimensions and it has checkpoints along the way. It will test your skill in multiple types of parkour. This is a relatively easy map but with some harder jumps. Don?t change your gamemode or cheat because that ruins the fun enjoy! I
Here is a YouTube Preview: https://youtu.be/XNCJMdplo_c
This map has some small sections only consisting of a few jumps before you reach the checkpoint but it also has a long end section at the end. This is able to be played in multiplayer or singleplayer!
This map was made by me, DapDap371 so if you are going to upload this onto Youtube make sure to Credit me.
